cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_ConfigurationIndex to 999 exceeds the valid range (0-255), causing invalid PRACH configuration and RACH setup failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_ConfigurationIndex 設定為 999 超過有效範圍（0-255），會導致無效的 PRACH 配置和 RACH 設定失敗。
